text: This video is based on Pre-trained models like Llama2 which has been trained on vast datasets and can generate high-quality text with minimal setup. Since the model is already trained, you don't need extensive computational resources.  The use case is suitable for applications where the quality of generation is paramount, and the context or data to be retrieved can be generalized or is contained within the training data of the LLM.   However,  Could you please create a video of the Customized Retrieval and Generation project(RAG)? This would be Ideal for applications where the retrieval needs are specific and the data sources are unique or require customized processing (e.g., legal documents, technical manuals, news articles).
